snippet.title: TRIANGLE STRATEGY - Final Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Command a group of warriors as Serenoa and decide the fate of your allies when the tactical RPG, TRIANGLE STRATEGY, launches soon!

A new demo of chapters 1-3 is available now on Nintendo eShop! Download today & transfer your save data when the game releases on 3/4:

https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/triangle-strategy-switch/

#TriangleStrategy #NintendoDirect #NintendoSwitch

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot
